<TEXT>
Industrials lost the momentum of the past few days and fell 44 to 6,058,
while the gold shares index added 16 at 1,983 as the price of bullion
remained firm. The overall index relinquished 53 at 5,202. Western Deep
moved ahead R1 to R187.
