FT  17 MAR 94 / UK Company News: Pan Atlas in black
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Pan Atlas Holdings, the travel company, returned to the black with pre-tax
profits of Pounds 57,114 for the year ended September 30 1993, against
Pounds 133,666 losses. Turnover increased from Pounds 4.51m to Pounds 4.68m.
